CRM Analytics REST API

Retrieve datasets by type of dataflow and get folder associations using the CRM Analytics REST API. Make GET requests with the CRM Analytics Connect API collection.

New and Changed CRM Analytics REST API Resources

Get a collection of datasets filtered by dataflow type
Make a GET request to the /wave/datasets resource.
Get a collection of folder associations
Make a GET request to the new /wave/folders/folderId/associations resource.

Request Bodies
Aggregate Flex Query Step Input: dataspace—The dataspace name for a Data Cloud object.
Cdp Step Input: dataspace—The dataspace name for a Data Cloud object.

Response Bodies
Aggregate Flex Step: dataspace—The dataspace name for a Data Cloud object.
Cdp Step: dataspace—The dataspace name for a Data Cloud object.
Wave Features: canWriteToDataCloud—Indicates whether Analytics data can write to Data Cloud data model objects.
